'RETURN ADDRESS' PRINTS OUT RETURNADDRESS LABELS. THE PRINTER CODESARE FOR THE IMAGEWRITER PRINTER. FOROTHER PRINTERS; CHANGE U$ TO THECODES FOR ULTRA-CONDENSED TYPE ANDS$ TO THE CODESTO SET THE SPACING TO EIGHT LINESPER INCH. CHANGE N$ TO YOUR NAME; A$TO YOUR STREET ADDRESS; AND T$ TOYOUR CITY; STATE; AND ZIP CODE. EACHOF THESE STRINGS MUST BE 21CHARACTERS ORLESS.